==Russian==

===Etymology===
Prefix ''[[при-]]'', indicating action or motion towards a terminal point, and ''[[ходить]]'', to walk or go
===Noun===
'''приходить''' ''v'' (imperfective)
# to [[come]], [[arrive]]; impf. of [[прийти]]
